###
### 1. Create a review for a product
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "productId": "{{productId}}",
    "rating": 5,
    "comment": "Excellent product! Highly recommended."
}

###
### 2. Create another review
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "productId": "{{productId}}",
    "rating": 4,
    "comment": "Good product, worth the price."
}

###
### 3. Create review - Invalid rating (should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "productId": "{{productId}}",
    "rating": 6,
    "comment": "Invalid rating"
}

###
### 4. Create review - Missing rating (should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "productId": "{{productId}}",
    "comment": "No rating provided"
}

###
### 5. Get all reviews (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 6. Get reviews for a specific product (uses $lookup to join with users)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 7. Get my reviews (uses $lookup to join with products)
GET {{baseUrl}}/my?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

